description: Steel City Pops is providing their famously tasty popsicle treats to the people of Austin, courtesy of this cool new cart. To ensure the finest quality, these gourmet paletas-inspired pops are made in small batches, all from completely fresh, all-natural, certified organic, and gluten-free ingredients. There’s a plethora of frozen fruity, creamy, and cookie concoctions, with flavors like Champagne White Tea, Strawberry Balsamic, Chai Latte, Coffee Brownie, and many more. Escape the heat and hop on over to Steel City Pops for a delightfully refreshing and guilt-free treat.
name: Steel City Pops
